<span class="go">2</span>
<span class="go">3</span>
<span class="go">1</span>
</pre></div>

          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>The last feature of functions we&rsquo;ll look at for now is
recursion.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code empty">
	        
            
